  "title": "Production Operator / Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description</u></p><p><u>Production Operator (PO)</u></p><ul><li>Operate production machinery  </li><li>Packing of chemicals into containers </li><li>Follow instructions of supervisor/manager     </li></ul><p><u>Warehouse assistant (WA</u>)<br /></p><ul><li>Assist in warehouse operations</li><li>Good in, Goods out </li><li>Maintain cleanliness</li></ul><p>         <br /><u>Requirement</u><br /></p><ul><li>Able to communicate, write and read English.</li><li>Able to carry and lift 30KG.</li><li>Chemical plant experience preferred for PO.</li><li>Warehouse experience preferred for WA.</li><li>Forklift license preferred for PO / must for WA.  </li><li> SGP / PR preferred but not a must.          </li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please call 62654700 ext.32 (Ms. Maslinda) to arrange for an interview.</p>",
